
HOW TO COMPILE ----------------------------------------------------------------
Ensure that you have the following libraries developement headers:
    OpenGL
    SDL
    libpng
and just run 'make'.


HOW TO RUN --------------------------------------------------------------------
Download the game data from http://everborn.sourceforge.net/download.html ,
unpack it somewhere.
From within the directory containing the data, run the 'everborn' executable.

There may be problems connecting to the server.
If so, spawn a separate server process running 'everborn dedicated' and, from
the main menu, select "Join Game".


HOW TO CREATE A RCFILE --------------------------------------------------------
Create a .everborn file in your home directory; inside you can specify some
default commands, for example:

#this is the location of the data files
set basedir /usr/local/games/everborn/

# this is to specify 1024x768 fullscreen mode
set screen 1024x768

# this is to specify windowed mode
set screen w
#or
set screen w640x480

# player name
set name Lord Wurstel

# debug: host a game and haste to OverlandMenu.
set fast yes


[EOF] -------------------------------------------------------------------------
